Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:01.64,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Otoč sa späť,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:04.35,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}te wo agete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:04.35,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}pozdvyhni ruku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:10.01,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}wakare no goaisatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:10.01,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}a pozdrav sa mi na rozlúčku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:13.75,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}donna kao
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:13.75,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Aký druh prejavu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:16.72,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}shiteiru no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:16.72,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}práve teraz máš?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:19.68,EDR,,0,0,0,,shiritai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:19.68,EDE,,0,0,0,,Ja chcem to vedieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:22.73,EDR,,0,0,0,,shiritakunai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:22.73,EDE,,0,0,0,,Ja nechcem to vedieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:25.86,EDR,,0,0,0,,bokura ga miteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:25.86,EDE,,0,0,0,,"My tu sme sledovaný."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:28.69,EDR,,0,0,0,,anata wa sou itta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:28.69,EDE,,0,0,0,,To je to, čo si povedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:34.74,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}sore wa kizuna to onaji de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:34.74,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Je to rovnaké ako okovy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:37.54,EDR,,0,0,0,,nagareru toki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:37.54,EDE,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem bojovať
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:40.54,EDR,,0,0,0,,sakaraenai no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:40.54,EDE,,0,0,0,,s tečúcim časom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:44.75,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}kawari takunakata
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:44.75,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0}Nechcela som túto zmenu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:48.34,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}I believe in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:48.34,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}Ja verím v lásku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:52.34,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}sayonara itoshii hito yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:52.34,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Zbohom buď láska moja jediná.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:56.60,EDR,,0,0,0,,senaka wo miokuri nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:56.60,EDE,,0,0,0,,Uvidíme sa niekde opodiaľ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:23:01.70,EDR,,0,0,0,,ima kidzuita no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:23:01.70,EDE,,0,0,0,,To som si hneď uvedomila.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:04.84,EDR,,0,0,0,,egao mo okotta kao mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:04.84,EDE,,0,0,0,,Tvoj úsmev a tvoj zamračený pohľad,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:08.73,EDR,,0,0,0,,yasashii mune mo koe mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:08.73,EDE,,0,0,0,,tvoje objatie a tvoj hlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.73,0:23:10.29,EDR,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.73,0:23:10.29,EDE,,0,0,0,,Aáách.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:14.56,EDR,,0,0,0,,itsumo soko ni atta kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:14.56,EDE,,0,0,0,,Budem vždy len s tebou.
